thread.title_full: TAXIBOX mobile self-storage reviewed by Hayden

author: Hayden
title: Hayden
text:
We used Taxibox a number of times whilst we renovated our house, stored our stuff whilst we moved in with my mother-in-law, the whole process was really painless. Would recommend Taxi Box to anyone.
Also, really impressed with the service our all the guys that have helped us.
